{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0d4c2085f3","title":"编辑说明","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"99cee22396","index":0,"year":1972,"month":10,"day":null,"articleId":"0d4c2085f3"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","name":"列宁选集 第一卷（1972年）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"列宁，人民出版社1972年","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"db1627a483","name":"中共中央马克思恩格斯列宁斯大林著作编译局"}]},"publication_details":{"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5128cb4d94","type":"paragraph","text":"编辑说明","index":0,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"0b433fcc5b","type":"paragraph","text":"《列宁选集》是1960年编辑出版的。为了适应广大读者学习马克思列宁主义的需要，现在我们重新出版这部选集，并对所选文章作了一些调整。","index":1,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"bce608f86c","type":"paragraph","text":"这部选集包括伟大革命导师列宁在各个时期的重要奢作。这些著作表明：列宁在反对帝国主义和形形色色的机会主义、修正主义的斗争中，继承、捍卫和发展了马克思主义，把马克思主义推进到一个新的历史阶段-—列宁主义阶段。","index":2,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"657d7163fa","type":"paragraph","text":"选集分为四卷，第一卷是1894-1907年的著作，第二卷是1908—1917年的著作，第三卷是1917--1919年的著作，第四卷是1919-1923年的著作。","index":3,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"b78a5cc5b4","type":"paragraph","text":"收入选集的著作，大部分是全文，只有小部分是摘录。所有文章都按写作或发表的时间顺序编排。","index":4,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"569144da03","type":"paragraph","text":"这次再版选集，对译文作了个别修改。每卷正文之后附有注释和人名索引。希望读者对这部选集的编译工作提出意见，以便再版时改进。","index":5,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"a3147ee06f","type":"paragraph","text":"中共中央马克思 恩格斯。","index":6,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"477a5a2de0","type":"paragraph","text":"列宁斯大林著作编译局","index":7,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"},{"id":"d8eac340d7","type":"paragraph","text":"1972年10月","index":8,"publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3"}],"page":{"id":"bd39939a74","publicationId":"175a6e6f-df63-678d-561b-ee7097c1bd9c","articleId":"0d4c2085f3","start":5,"end":5}}}},"__N_SSG":true}